{
  "title": "Sick-Day Silky Saudi-Arabian Dish Pudding",
  "description": "A soothing, grassy pudding for those tough Saudi-Arabian days. Made with heavy cream, caramelized and Whole30-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi-Arabian",
  "diet": [
    "Whole30",
